select CMOC_YEAR, CMOC_COUNTRY, cast( sum (CMOC_CURRBALFACTACC) as decimal (13,2)) , cast( sum (CMOC_CURRBALSPECIALACC) as decimal (13,2)), cast( sum (CMOC_TOTNINVOUTFACTACC) as decimal (9,0)), cast( sum (CMOC_TOTNINVOUTSPECACC) as decimal (9,0)) from :1 where CMOC_ADMNO = :2 and CMOC_CLNTNO = :3 and CMOC_YEAR between :4 and :5 and CMOC_MONTH between 1 and :6 and CMOC_CURRENCY = ':7' group by CMOC_YEAR, CMOC_COUNTRY for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
